          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Unfortunately, many think to own an exotic car means you must buy something Italian. While you could do that, if you’re looking to stand out from the crowd and be more original, the Audi R8 is a great option to consider. There aren’t too many German supercars out there, and that’s too bad considering how much of a sophisticated monster this car can be.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
